    schema:activitiesWorkload "100%"@es ;
    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/93000963/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description """This course will focus in the design of real world medical technology development. It will consist of an intensive and practical continuation of contents of DTB course to understand and define significant unmet medical needs and designing new medical technologies to address them. Two main issues will be covered in this course: prototyping and creation of a business plan.

The course is developed with some large group sessions, but mostly tutor sessions with a group of 5-6 students, assigned according to the subject of the project to be developed."""@es ;
    schema:director <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/p.sanchez%40upm.es> ;
    schema:inLanguage "Inglés/Castellano"@es ;
    schema:instructor <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/ap.seiffert%40upm.es>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/enriquejavier.gomez%40upm.es>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/giuseppe.fico%40upm.es>,
